 @{" " link "'#toc0'/MAIN"}Name rzxcheck - Check the signature in a ZX Spectrum RZX file @{" " link "'#toc1'/MAIN"}Synopsis @{"b"}rzxcheck@{"ub"} @{"i"}rzxfile@{"ui"}... 

@{" " link "'#toc2'/MAIN"}Description Rzxcheck verifies the digital signature found in a Sinclair ZX Spectrum RZX input recording file. @{" " link "'#toc3'/MAIN"}Options @{"i"}rzxfile@{"ui"} specifies an input recording file whose signature is to be verified. @{" " link "'#toc4'/MAIN"}Bugs None known. @{" " link "'#toc5'/MAIN"}See Also @{" " link "'fuse.1'/MAIN"}@{"i"}fuse@{"ui"}(1) , @{" " link "'fuse-utils.1'/MAIN"}@{"i"}fuse-utils@{"ui"}(1) , @{" " link "'rzxdump.1'/MAIN"}@{"i"}rzxdump@{"ui"}(1) , @{" " link "'rzxtool.1'/MAIN"}@{"i"}rzxtool@{"ui"}(1) 

